            <description><![CDATA[别急，咱是说：这些人呀，可能听力真不行——<br><br>那个让你社死，不管在哪都扯着大嗓门的爸妈；那个耳背的村口大爷，你说要去拿个快递，他听成你在深圳有块地……<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>他们耳朵里的世界，不像你的那样清晰。<br><br>成天戴耳机、喜欢用棉签掏耳朵等不良习惯，使听力损伤也越来越年轻化。听力损伤不可逆转，越早诊疗效果越好。带他们去查查听力，给身边的人一个善意提醒，再拖下去，真的不行哦~ <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%88%B1%E8%80%B3%E6%97%A5%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#爱耳日#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%90%AC%E5%8A%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%8F%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%90%AC%E5%8A%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不正确的掏耳朵真的会影响听力#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4875240061468764" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hbmr7vpleaj217w0oqwlr.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/fQRYCdvxgx083A3CH2I0010412013iWZ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1052x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677878360&amp;ssig=ZS4NjrujZq&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/z0VeuWU2gx083A3C0wIo01041200xPFu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=700x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677878360&amp;ssig=YyTPT38Pp%2B&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/tAhh